  35:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Enable the clock for the UART GPIOs.
  36:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Configure these UART pins as alternate function pull-up.
  37:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) NVIC configuration if you need to use interrupt process (HAL_UART_Transmit_IT()
