  44:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_uart.c ****                 are managed using the macros __HAL_UART_ENABLE_IT() and __HAL_UART_DISABLE_IT()
  45:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_uart.c ****                 inside the transmit and receive processes.
