1104:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_uart.c ****   * @param huart   UART handle.
1105:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_uart.c ****   * @param pData   Pointer to data buffer (u8 or u16 data elements).
1106:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_uart.c ****   * @param Size    Amount of data elements (u8 or u16) to be sent.
